This year is the first time in a decade I am not travelling to the US willingly because I am genuinely worried that for some reason I could be denied entry for whatever reason - which obviously would not make any sense like I have been here 10+ times and I left every time never overstaying my visit or anything but I am genuinely worried that it could happen. That fear alone is enough to deter me besides the fact that I am also worried about what is going to happen tomorrow with this unhinged administration.

I am genuinely sad the US is an amazing country with so much to offer but well it is time to explore other parts of the worlds now I guess. The issue I see with this is also people me included might not return to the US as soon as the administration changes while protesting the US and travelling somewhere else they might fall in love with a different place/ different country / different continent and continue spending their money elsewhere even if the US returns back to how it used to be.",2026-05-03T11:13:22Z,2026-05-03T11:13:22Z,1,False,1.0,2026-05-04T02:02:19.351462
