Tourism,-IOhTUF2W0A,UgxFTltW0SmS_T6OHn14AaABAg,,@CapulloSpawn,"As a Swiss, buying a burner phone so i can enter a country, because i used my free speech in my country, doesn't make any sense to me, and my fellow citizens. 
