Tourisme,tQG5jBBGn2Q,UgxnPhTkB3q6zCOO3O94AaABAg.AWMu3f4DJQKAWMwX7Bt7xQ,UgxnPhTkB3q6zCOO3O94AaABAg,@kaicoetzee7610,"I wish people like this could truly understand what it means to move through the world as an African. Not just the visa walls — but the assumptions people make about you, the way you're treated at borders, in airports, in shops abroad, the way your passport is looked at twice, the way you have to work three times as hard to be taken half as seriously. It's not a complaint. It's just a reality that most people never have to think about, because their history made sure they wouldn't.",2026-05-04T00:55:10Z,2026-05-04T00:55:10Z,0,True,,2026-05-04T02:03:25.721811
